title: Babyscripts MyJourney™️
description: Babyscripts is a virtual care program supporting maternal healthcare management. It is prescribed by healthcare providers to expectant mothers at the start of their pregnancy to support their reproductive and sexual health up through one year postpartum. The mobile app delivers custom content to patients, from their OB team, on a weekly basis to guide them through their pregnancy with practice-specific, provider-approved medical references and education related to behaviors that support a happy and healthy pregnancy, including guidance and tracking tools for nutrition and weight management.
